{"type": "article", "id": 25312, "title": "指甲油包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-12T06:35:05Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702111712Xglc47kPA2wfMNVW.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是法国高跟鞋品牌 Christian Louboutin（克里斯提·鲁布托）推出的礼盒装指甲油系列。他们最开始为蓝、白、黄三种颜色的指甲油设计了黄蓝色的包装。蓝色和黄色像颜料一样随意点缀在包装上，鲜艳而有张力。他们后来增加了另外两种是夏威夷风格的热带植物和芙蓉花，只在背景有白色或黑色的区别，很应景。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111710uDpeSlLG73aQ9Vzf.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070211171071WVMR0XYG8ToPKb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111711iEJ5chrHNSUtBZz2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.504\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111711koeUZWHdPLfuBFt0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62962963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}